content:
 - Gushyira umwana mu gituza cy’umubyeyi akimara
kuvuka no kumwonsa mu isaha ya mbere akivuka;
 - Gushyigikira umutwe w’umwana igihe umufashe ;
 - Kurambura ingingo z’umwana no kumuguyaguya
kenshimu rwego rwo kumuha urukundo;
 - Kwita ku mwana no kumuba ha n’igihe wowe wumva  utameze neza;
 - Kumwonsa kenshi ntamfashabere ahawe, cyane cyane  igihe abishatse;
 - Guhanagura umwana neza igihe yitumye,kumuhindurira  warangiza
   ugakaraba intoki n’amazi meza n’isabune;
 - Kuvugisha umwana, no kumuririmbira kenshi  gashoboka;
 - Kumugaragariza no kumuha urukundo buri gihe;
 - Kujyana umwana ku Kigo Nderabuzima mu cyumweru  cya mbere akivuka na
   nyuma y’ibyumweru bitandatu  avutse;
 - Kubahiriza gahunda y’ikingira.
